manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Parents, teachers, and kids looking for that perfect indoor/outdoor activity that promotes learning through play, will love the convenience, durability, and entertainment offered by the PlayVibe Magnetic Tiles Set.

This colorful set is guaranteed to be a hit at children’s birthday parties, family reunions, and more. Designed for durability and safety, our set uses non-toxic, premium materials and magnets – featuring smooth, rounded edges, so children 3 and older can play and build all day long. The magnetic tiles also help develop critical skills including motor skills, hand-eye coordination, cognitive ability, problem-solving, counting, and critical thinking. Our premium magnets insure a strong hold for ease of assembly. Each shape features magnets along the edges that snap together so that shapes can be assembled into hundreds of different creations, including cars, trains, castles, and more. After hours of building, the creations can easily be broken down and stored. Materials: Heavy Duty, Brightly Colored Plastic. Rubber, Magnets.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good value and sturdy
reviews.reviewText: These seem sturdy and work well. Easy to assemble and my 3.5 year old kids are enjoying them. These are more affordable than other options, but I think you have to buy two of them to really make something grand. There aren't enough square pieces and too many triangle pieces. I bought another set of 60 and that seems like a good amount.Update. After several weeks of play, some of the pieces are breaking apart and the magnets are coming out. I'll still leave it at 5 stars because they're cheaper than comparable brands and they held up fairly well after heavy use.
